                        <desc>Fine and carefull.
                        <persName role="scribe" ref="PRS14616MalkeaKrestos">Malkǝʾa Krǝstos</persName> is mentioned as the scribe in the <ref target="#coloph1"/>. His name is also
                           written, in red, in the middle of the bottom margin on <locus target="#3r"/>.</desc>
                        
                        <list type="abbreviations">
                           <item>
                              <abbr>ይ፡ ካ፡</abbr> for <expan>ይቤ፡ ካህን፡ </expan> (<locus target="#32vb"/>)</item>
