                           <q xml:lang="gez">ወነግሠ፡ <persName ref="PRS8550sardaDe"><roleName type="title">ንጉሥ፡</roleName> መለክ፡ ሰገድ፡</persName>  እንዘ፡ ወልደ፡
                              ፲ወ፫፡ ዓመት፡ ወ፯፡ አውራኅ። ወበ፭፡ ዓመት፡ ሞተት፡ <persName ref="PRS8276SablaWa"><roleName type="title">ኢቴ፡</roleName> ሰብለ፡ ወንጌል፤</persName> ወበ፲ወ፪፡ ዓመት፡ ሞተ፡
                              <persName ref="PRS5112harbo"><roleName type="title"> አዝማች፡</roleName> ሀርቦ</persName>። ወበ፲ወ፬፡ {ዓመት፡}ሞተ፡ <persName ref="PRS7278Muhammad"> መሐመድ፡</persName> ወበ፲ወ፯፡ ዓመት፡ ሞተ፡ <persName ref="PRS10343Yeshaq">
